## üì¶ Installation

### üì¶ From PyPI (Recommended)
```bash
pip install python-android-avd-manager
```

### üöß From Source
```bash
git clone https://github.com/jwoirhaye/python-android-avd-manager-python.git
cd python-android-avd-manager
pip install -e .
```

